    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Seats with reed and cane backs, used by the tlahtoani (ruler) of Nahua altepemeh (polities).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
